# --- hw3 CI essentials: re-included so GitHub Actions can run ---
# .github is excluded as a directory above, so re-include the dir first, then its contents.
!/.github/
!/.github/workflows/
!/.github/workflows/**
# commit hw3 lockfiles so CI can use `npm ci`
!hw3/server/package-lock.json
!hw3/client/package-lock.json
# commit hw3 server tests (line `**/*test*` would otherwise ignore them)
!hw3/server/test/
!hw3/server/test/**